//   The same <ProductCard> markup powers Best Sellers and Our Collections, so a
//   product object is interchangeable between the two arrays.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

// TODO_HUMMICO: Replace these 4 placeholder best-sellers with real products
// (name, description, price, Etsy listing URL, and a product photo).
